article.description: — Johni Broome had 18 points and 10 rebounds to lift Morehead State to a 77-52 win over Austin Peay on Saturday, the Eagles' 12th consecutive home victory.
article.headline: Broome lifts Morehead St. over Austin Peay 77-52
article.linkText: Broome lifts Morehead St. over Austin Peay 77-52
article.story: MOREHEAD, Ky. -- — Johni Broome had 18 points and 10 rebounds to lift Morehead State to a 77-52 win over Austin Peay on Saturday, the Eagles' 12th consecutive home victory. Skyelar Potter had 13 points for Morehead State (19-6, 11-1 Ohio Valley Conference). Jaylon Hall added six assists. Elijah Hutchins-Everett had 11 points for the Governors (7-13, 3-7). The Eagles improve to 2-0 against the Governors for the season. Morehead State defeated Austin Peay 66-55 on Jan. 8. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
